TARDIS
======

A program for time tracking.


Overview
--------

Records the current time and project string entered by inserting into an entry
table in Sqlite3.


Schema
------

The schema is a couple of tables. The important one is:

CREATE TABLE entries(
  id integer primary key autoincrement,
  start datetime default current_timestamp,
  project text,
  description text,
  end datetime
);


